fm: int findKthLargest(vector<int> &nums, int k) {         priority_queue<int, vector<int>, greater<>> min_heap;         for (auto &m : nums) {             if (min_heap.size() < k || min_heap.top() < m)                 min_heap.push(m);             if (min_heap.size() > k)                 min_heap.pop();         }         return min_heap.top();     }

fc: class Solution { public:     vector<vector<int>> combinationSum3(int k, int n) {         vector<vector<int>> ret;         vector<int> temp;         helper(k, n, ret, temp, 1);         return ret;     }      void helper(int n, int sum, vector<vector<int>> &ret, vector<int> &temp, int index) {         if (sum == 0 && n == 0) {             ret.push_back(temp);             return;         }         for (int i = index; i <= 9; ++i) {             if (sum - i < 0)                 break;             temp.push_back(i);             helper(n - 1, sum - i, ret, temp, i + 1);             temp.pop_back();         }     } };

fm: bool containsNearbyDuplicate(vector<int> &nums, int k) {         int n = nums.size();         if (n <= 1)             return false;         map<int, int> dup;         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {             if ((dup.find(nums[i]) != dup.end()) && (abs(i - dup[nums[i]]) <= k))                 return true;             dup[nums[i]] = i;         }         return false;     }
